WEBVTT

00:10:59.712 --> 00:11:01.149
begin to study what they love,

00:11:01.173 --> 00:11:02.352
love what they study,

00:11:02.376 --> 00:11:03.759
follow their passion ...

00:11:04.577 --> 00:11:07.046
getting stimulated by their intelligence,

00:11:07.070 --> 00:11:10.507
follow paths of inquiry
that they really want to.

00:11:10.848 --> 00:11:15.298
After all, it was Eric and Kevin,

00:11:15.322 --> 00:11:16.490
two years ago,

00:11:17.498 --> 00:11:20.930
just exactly these kinds of young men,

00:11:20.954 --> 00:11:22.976
who prompted me and worked with me,

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:24.561
and still do,

00:11:24.585 --> 00:11:28.271
in the study of indebted
students in America.

00:11:29.272 --> 00:11:30.803
Thank you for your attention.